# Runtime command safety (containers)

## Rule (guardrail)

This repo is containerized and many runtime commands are environment-specific.

- Do NOT run Node/npm commands automatically (e.g. `node`, `npm`, `npx`).
- Do NOT run PHP/Composer commands automatically (e.g. `php`, `composer`, `php bin/magento`, `vendor/bin/phpunit`).
- Do NOT run Docker commands automatically (e.g. `docker`, `docker compose`).

Instead:
- Ask which container/service to use and the working directory.
- Prefer stable, repeatable command shapes.

## Runbook

See `runtime-commands-containers` skill.
